 red;\">機場鐵路全線為四線化設計</span>，也因為中國政府認為建築費過高而改為部份路段雙軌設計；<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新市鎮發展方面，原本計劃的大蠔及小蠔兩個山谷都會發展為新市鎮</span>，亦因為中國政府認為建築費過高而擱置。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府真係勁<br />\n家下大小蠔都無人住, 又唔發展"},{"pid":"9d74e326e62af2c88228370de5cd373e311f5e78","tid":857263,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef2adfe9cbb52f3a7750b569b334510f4320b3a3","tid":857263,"uid":116572,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"dd1f5624369e3297eef6e680a93f04ba8f3a91a0","tid":857263,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6de8f7e6826b903669424d49c80cdf87556498c1","tid":857263,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"按返消費物價指數計<br />\n等如今日4500億<br />\n <a href=\"https://invest.hket.com/article/2180137/%E3%80%90%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A2018%E3%80%91%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BCvs%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E5%9C%92%20%E5%85%A9%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E5%B1%B1%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2180137%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A2018%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BCvs%25E7%258E%25AB%25E7%2591%25B0%25E5%259C%2592%2520%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%258A%2583%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25BC%2583%20&d=sAFpH7DsjKt%2BiF%2FuezB%2BmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c2913d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://invest.hket.com/article/2180137/%E3%80%90%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A2018%E3%80%91%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BCvs%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0%E5%9C%92%20%E5%85%A9%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC%E5%B1%B1%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83 </a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"good<br />\n<strong>機場連<ins>兩條跑道</strong>,</ins> 當年707億=<strong>今日~2,121億</strong>,仲已經係當年全世界最貴<br />\n今日<ins>一條跑道</ins><strong>1,400億</strong><br />\n<img 